<< Wait until the explosion happens (usually 6-8 turns) >>

    w. get into webbing. wait. wait. wait. wait. wait. wait. wait. wait.
    wait. wait. wait. wait. wait. get out of webbing. take all. open door.
    u. u. u. u. u. n. ne. e. e. take id card. drop all except kit. e. s. s.
    s. sw. take all. drop battery. ne. n. n. n. n. put bar over crevice. s.
    e. drop all except key. press blue button. press red button. w. w. w.
    unlock padlock with key. take padlock. open door. n.
    drop key and padlock. take ladder. s. e. e. n. n. drop ladder.
    extend ladder. put ladder over rift. n. w. open desk.
    put kitchen card and upper card into pocket. w. open desk.
    put shuttle card into pocket. e. e. s. s. s. e. take kit and flask.
    open kit. eat red goo. w. s. s. s. se. open robot. close robot.
    turn on robot. nw. n. n. e. take bedistor. w. n. e. n.
    slide upper card through slot. press up button. wait. wait. s. ne.

<< Remember COLOR of flashing light >>

    sw. n. press down button. wait. wait. s. w. s. s. s. s.
    put flask under spout. press [COLOR] button.
    take flask. n. n. n. n. e. n. slide upper card through slot.
    press up button. wait. wait. s. ne. pour liquid into funnel.

<< Repeat with new COLOR until the enunciator panel goes dark. Note >>
<< that you will only get in 2 iterations before you need to sleep, >>
<< so if you need more than that sleep (below), then do the kitchen >>
<< sequence, then come back and do the last iteration               >>

    sw. n. press down button. wait. wait. s. w. w. s. get in bed. wait.
    get up. take all. eat green goo. drop kit. n. w. s. take canteen.
    slide kitchen card through slot. s. open canteen.
    put canteen into niche. press button. take canteen. close canteen. n.
    drop kitchen card. n. e. e.

<< Go south and do the last flask/liquid/funnel iteration here if   >>
<< needed.  Otherwise say "e." and continue                         >>

    drop flask and upper card. take laser and pliers. s.
    slide lower card through slot. press down button. wait. wait. wait.
    drop lower card. n. e. s. e. slide shuttle card through slot.
    push lever up. wait. wait. wait. wait. wait. wait. wait. wait. wait.
    wait. wait. pull lever down. pull lever down. wait. wait. wait. wait.
    wait. wait. wait. wait. wait. wait. wait. drop shuttle card. w. n. e. e.
    ne. e. e. n. open lid. take fused bedistor with pliers.
    put good bedistor into cube. close cube. open canteen. drink liquid.
    drop pliers and fused bedistor and canteen. s. w. w. n.

<< Make sure Floyd is present; if not wait for him to show up >>

    floyd, go n.
    floyd, get shiny fromitz board.
    s. e. n. open panel. take second board. put shiny board into socket.
    close panel. s. e. s. s. s.

<< Wait until Floyd enters and sees the computer light >>.

    ne. open bio-lab door. se. e. look through window. open door.
    close door. wait. open door. close door. put mini card into pocket. w.
    open door. w. s. put battery into laser. n. sw. s.
    slide mini card through slot. type 384. e. n. n. turn dial to 1.
    fire laser at speck.

<< Continue to fire the laser at the speck until the speck vaporizes >>

    turn dial to 6. s. fire laser at microbe.

<< Continue to fire the laser until the laser feels "very warm" >>.

    throw laser over edge. s. w. n. open desk. wear gas mask.
    press white button. press red button. open office door. w.
    open lab door. w. w. open door. w. w. w. s. s. press button. wait. wait.
    wait. n.